items.title: Playoff-hunting Brewers blank Bucs again
items.summary: Chase Anderson continued his string of solid starts by pitching six scoreless innings, and Domingo Santana backed him with a solo homer in a 1-0 win over the Pirates on Tuesday at PNC Park.

items.title: Grandal's HR gives Dodgers new club record
items.summary: An All-Star in his first season with the Dodgers and the unquestioned starting catcher in his second year, Yasmani Grandal, now in his third season with the club, is battling a slump that jeopardizes his playing time in the postseason.
